# Java
target/         → compiled Java output folder, auto-generated, no need to push
*.class         → compiled Java class files
*.jar           → packaged Java files
.mvn/           → Maven wrapper files, not needed in repo
# React
node_modules/   → thousands of dependency files, never push these
                  anyone cloning your repo runs npm install to get them
build/          → production build output, auto-generated
dist/           → same, another common build output folder
# Environment
.env                        → contains secret keys like Claude API key
                              NEVER push this to GitHub
application-local.properties → local database passwords, keep private
# IDE
.idea/    → IntelliJ settings, personal to your machine
.vscode/  → VS Code settings, personal to your machine
*.iml     → IntelliJ module files
.DS_Store → Mac system file, irrelevant to the project